        {
            "id": 6008969,
            "title": "〈台幣〉降息預期升溫美元轉弱 連2升收29.922元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>有「小非農」之稱的美國 ADP 就業報告出爐，5 月數據遜於預期，美國總統川普再次呼籲聯準會盡速降息，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DXY\">美元指數</a>應聲走弱。<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元匯率今 (5) 日跟隨主要亞幣走強，一度升值超過 1 角，但隨著美元買盤湧現，升幅逐漸收斂，終場收在 29.922 元，升值 3 分，為連 2 揚，台北及元太外匯市場總成交值放大至 21.23 億美元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008969%2Fl%2F68665e7094cbab6c5e8d336913b5dba0.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台幣〉降息預期升溫美元轉弱 連2升收29.922元。(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元今天開盤價為 29.92 元，早盤一度勁揚 1.02 角，升抵 29.85 元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外匯交易員指出，出口商近來每日幾乎都有固定掛單賣匯，不過，央行會適時進場提供流動性，加上政府基金、油款等也進場買美元，不至於出現 5 月初的恐慌性拋匯的失序場面，而外資維持雙向進出，無明確方向。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>匯銀人士表示，近期國際消息紛雜，美國就業數據不如預期，美國對進口鋼鐵與鋁材的加徵關稅生效，市場持續關注各國與美方的關稅談判，並聚焦本周五即將公布的非農就業報告，以進一步分析聯準會降息步調是否有所調整。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>根據央行統計，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DXY\">美元指數</a>今天下跌 0.32%，主要受到川普喊話盡速降息影響，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/krwusd\">韓元</a>因選出新總統持續升值 0.63%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>勁揚 0.52%，新加坡幣升值 0.33%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>升值 0.1%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>小升 0.08%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
